Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:08.25,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All units, widen the gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:15.09,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That speed and maneuverability is indeed a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:15.82,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:19.54,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There is a certain pattern that fellow moves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:21.87,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A frontal attack will come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:23.66,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He won't make a pinpoint attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:29.63,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Once his attack is evaded, he will quickly move to launch his next attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.34,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Analyze his movement data.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:33.42,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,X57!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:42.68,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. In such a situation, his next action... will be to jump back to widen the distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:44.35,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The coordinate is X23!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:45.39,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:46.81,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:51.42,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,He evaded my triple thrust?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:52.03,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,However...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:06.46,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:08.29,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,It's... Suzaku-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:10.07,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.41,0:01:12.55,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, the orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:14.48,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us your next orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:15.28,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:18.38,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Everything so far was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:23.96,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:07.82,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,In Britannia, I had my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:10.93,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I had vassals and classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:14.16,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:24.18,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That was why, to me, Suzaku was the first friend I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.19,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It was a sudden attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:44.46,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\fscy80}The Japanese defense force was thrown into combat against the Britannian Army who deployed the Mobile Humanoid Combat Armored Knights, the KnightMare Frames.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.68,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They were completely overwhelmed and defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:54.58,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to be handed over to someone else's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.45,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's another Kururugi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:59.84,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This time, we're going to the main one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.76,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.26,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:09.18,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:12.89,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? There's a weird smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:15.47,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's because we're near a garbage dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:16.00,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.55,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:22.61,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:26.55,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,910)}going to destroy Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.27,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:32.96,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:33.87,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.85,CG ON,???01,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:40.17,CG ON,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,He calls himself Zero and is standing against the procession!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.03,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:44.95,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I swore back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:52.81,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,that I wouldn't forgive Britannia for taking away Mother... Nunnally's eyes and legs, and the life I had with Suzaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:59.83,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,And... in order to turn the world into a place where Nunnally can live in happily...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:03.65,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I shall destroy the world and change everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.79,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.78,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll announce it, Orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:10.62,CG ON,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:18.18,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be publicly announced if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.70,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want that to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:20.40,CG ON,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.05,CG ON,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:25.13,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You will do your best to set us free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.70,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Do the same for that man over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.06,CG ON,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.48,CG ON,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Hand that man over to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:39.48,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.48,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jeremiah, what are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:44.04,CG ON,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Hand him over! No one is to interfere in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.25,CG ON,Kewell,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.40,CG ON,Kewell,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:49.20,CG ON,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Kewell, this is an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.70,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,You despicable Eleven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.83,CG ON,Viletta,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jeremiah, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.77,CG ON,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you not to interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.55,CG ON,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best to set them free!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.72,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,People!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:11.05,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Fear us or seek us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:14.06,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We are... the Order of the Black Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:21.19,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,When those with power attack those without, we will appear once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:25.90,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how great the power of the enemy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.14,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Those with power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.90,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Fear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.64,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Those without power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:36.91,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Seek us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:42.38,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The world shall be judged by us, the Order of the Black Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:46.51,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If someone wins, the fighting will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:48.01,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:55.00,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That was why I became Zero and created the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.83,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,340)}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:01.59,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Lelouch! You were asleep just now, weren't you?! I saw you stop working!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.69,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you don't need to hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:07.74,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The vice president of the Ashford Academy Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:10.53,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That is the identity I assumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:15.08,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I spent my life idly as a Britannian student.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:21.27,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The only problem was that merrymaking president who likes to cause trouble for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:27.84,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,"Man and Woman Role-reversal Festival", "Absolute Silence Party", "Cat Festival", "Orange Day".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.21,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I can still forgive her for those.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:31.17,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I will go along with it if she says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:36.00,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, that "Day as a Grade School Student" was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:39.54,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No... Nunnally seemed to have enjoyed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:43.73,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine as long as she's happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.40,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:50.99,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we came to this academy, Nunnally has begun to smile a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:55.03,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Suzaku is here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:59.94,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, who had been separated from us ever since that summer seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:04.36,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I mustn't let them know that I'm Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:07.77,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If that happened, such a normal life would be completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.59,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.26,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.76,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:22.16,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I must protect them at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.82,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.16,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Zero's secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.04,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Information about the Geass....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.30,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Then he..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:37.63,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:40.41,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the mask that Zero wears?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.29,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,No way. In a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.75,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.19,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,440)}Forget about what you just saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.32,CG ON,Both,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}Yeah, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.78,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll use it when necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.62,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,This is President Milly Ashford of the Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.39,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.31,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:03.69,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Catch the cat that is running through the school right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:05.27,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,All club activities will be canceled temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.75,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Any clubs that participate will have their funding increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:11.52,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.89,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:14.25,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,You're chasing the cat too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.18,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's up above?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.48,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:21.70,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:24.04,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,But the student council president said to capture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.29,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind her, just go back! I'll catch the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.65,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm better at physical activity!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.37,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That one time that chick ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.92,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring up old stories now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:33.82,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That was only seven years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.05,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:39.14,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, you're an idiot that's thinking with only his muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.64,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:43.89,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.89,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:49.85,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That guy... he was way more selfish in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:54.23,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.68,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:04.24,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.16,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:21.68,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was moving according to my calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:26.10,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,0)}Until the appearance of that white KnightMare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:30.48,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Guided Weapon, Z-01 Lancelot will use the sand board.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:34.51,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,You will accelerate at max speed and head up to save the Governor-General by liquifying the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:35.65,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:40.62,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-kun, there's something that I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.11,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:46.08,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,You really hate it when people die, yet you're in the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.57,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:49.83,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the army so that they won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:53.27,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,That contradiction might kill you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.19,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I'm sorry. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.92,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot, launching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:17.17,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Governor-General, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.28,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:21.07,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Again... This guy again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.67,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Guren Mk. II, destroy that white armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.20,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,His ability to break through is a hindrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:28.97,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.23,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,If I defeat this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.85,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Such weapons...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.69,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It blocked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:10.24,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:12.87,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, follow the escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.76,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This will degrade into a battle of attrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:15.82,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:20.44,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Governor-General!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:21.78,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,You chase after Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:22.66,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.42,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that my Energy Filler has run low.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:25.33,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:25.93,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.77,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,To the head trailer of the special envoy:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:49.49,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I've discovered Zero and am going to capture him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.51,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.60,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.55,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:14.23,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, that fellow was already different back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.54,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He was calling himself "Boku". {Desu~ Desu~ Desu~}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.71,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he used "Ore" in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:25.67,CG ON,,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, let's keep pretending to be strangers while we're at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:29.89,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Although the police are incompetent now, they can join the police and change them from the inside, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:33.82,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,The Order of the Black Knights... the way that Zero acts is too despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.50,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,They don't start things by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:39.08,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,They only ride the coattails of others and disturb the situation.{Dear QC people: Coattails is one}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.96,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,They think of themselves as judges and indulge in their victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.44,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing changes by doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:46.67,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's worthless to achieve results by using the wrong methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:53.13,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The Suzaku I met for the first time seven years ago was much more selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:14:00.14,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He was upright and proud to be Japanese, even shedding tears because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:03.69,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(920,0)}If you think about it from another perspective, not everything has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:07.30,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is indeed something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.07,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.23,CG ON,Mao,0000,0000,0000,,You want to save people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:17.54,CG ON,Mao,0000,0000,0000,,The thing you want to save is your own heart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.48,CG ON,Mao,0000,0000,0000,,You hope that you would die while doing so, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:23.86,CG ON,Mao,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you always place yourself on the verge of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.98,CG ON,Mao,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness is there just for self-justification!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:32.45,CG ON,Mao,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a spoiled brat that wished to be punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.95,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Mao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.60,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:36.75,CG ON,Mao,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.94,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I finally know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:43.83,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why you changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:44.95,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:47.90,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:56.54,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, you were keeping such a big secret and couldn't tell anyone about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.88,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You've been bearing it all this time, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.55,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Father...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:22.81,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible, you should have died...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.82,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,No! That wasn't my intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.03,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I... I!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:39.00,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice but to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:46.89,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.84,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:51.07,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.97,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry... escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.89,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Be it binding himself down with rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.04,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,460)}or becoming a Britannian soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.41,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,they were all done for atonement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.31,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.52,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:11.99,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Britannia is not a country worth serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.86,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:19.04,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to change Britannia into a worthwhile country from the inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:19.95,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Change it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:24.73,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I think that it's worthless to achieve results by using the wrong methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:26.40,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:28.75,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,In about an hour, the court-martial will start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.98,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:34.22,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That trial is rigged to judge you as the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.34,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The police, the witnesses, even the lawyers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.76,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, those are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:43.64,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't go, the accusations against the Elevens and honorary Britannians will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.28,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But you will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:46.32,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:47.77,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:52.19,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, my friend told me that a lot. "You're an idiot."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:55.49,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that's my weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:59.61,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I want to capture you, but if I do that here, I would probably face retaliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:03.11,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm to be killed, then I would rather die for the sake of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:05.67,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,But, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:07.83,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:12.60,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What a stupid fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:15.14,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:19.85,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However... However that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:24.42,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were suitable to be Nunnally's knight because that's the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:31.01,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't remain by Nunnally's side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:35.63,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you fighting if you are not Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:37.51,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:39.34,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The destruction of Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:44.33,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you are capable of doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.27,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:49.87,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because I have a reason that I must do it at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:55.84,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If things proceed as planned, there will eventually be a day I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.14,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Are you embarking on it? The path of carnage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:04.02,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If that is my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.61,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I need it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:11.87,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Someone Nunnally can bare her heart to, a person I can trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.13,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yet..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:22.12,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.25,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.00,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,It's... Suzaku-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.73,CG ON,???01,0000,0000,0000,,It's an Eleven! If I remember correctly, that's Kururugi Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:34.09,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,The one from His Excellency, Clovis's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.43,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Why is an Eleven inside a KnightMare?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:36.43,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:37.95,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the video transmission! If this goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:38.99,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:39.43,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:41.80,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:44.31,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it can still move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.06,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Suzaku-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.94,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah. Toudou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:56.28,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still wish to continue living even after breaking your own principles?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:58.04,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Are you disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:00.61,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you execute me as planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.07,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:05.61,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:07.16,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You should be beside Nunnally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.40,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.16,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come here to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:13.92,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Have you degenerated into a useless brat who's satisfied with the present?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:17.12,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's meaningless to go against the current society.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:20.17,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,A power that accepts it and tries to change it is then truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:20.92,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.94,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:23.92,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should travel down that path!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:24.51,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:31.36,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Be it victory or defeat, you won't achieve anything unless you do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:33.94,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,The same applies whether it's at the national or personal level!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:35.68,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:41.76,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, are we going to capture him or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:42.41,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.45,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Warrant Suzaku, release the Haken Booster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.64,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,The password is my favorite thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:53.90,CG ON,Nagisa,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:54.42,CG ON,Shougo,0000,0000,0000,,What the..?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.08,CG ON,Kosetsu,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.55,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:04.72,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:07.29,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Stop... Continuing this fight is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.08,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We have achieved our objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:11.14,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Use route three...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.10,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We will retreat immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:23.74,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:28.12,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I will answer the question raised earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:31.16,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,You were wondering whether I had decided on who would be my knight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:36.21,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,The one I have decided on to be my knight is the person over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.78,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Warrant Officer Kururugi Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:43.22,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.83,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku is going to be Euphemia's knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:49.47,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:53.60,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(840,0)}There is a certain person who is seeing that the investigation be carried out properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:57.28,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That person said: "If you're seventeen, you should go to school".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:20:59.62,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:06.51,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The person with authority back then was the third princess of Britannia, Euphemia li Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.58,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Suzaku is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:13.33,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, back then too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:16.67,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The one you wanted to save then was Euphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.42,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:21.06,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, everything makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:25.27,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, you've chosen Euphie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:27.73,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Not us, but Euphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:33.08,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I can do, but there's no need for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:38.10,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is already within my reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:42.65,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,since I know that the pilot of that white armor is Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:17.84,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:19.25,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your constant support.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:22.77,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This time, the second opening, "Kaidoku Funou"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:26.72,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,the ending, "Mosaic Kakera", the original soundtrack CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:28.15,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A special calling card produced for the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:32.96,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,and a Cheese-kun cubic puzzle stolen from C.C..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:34.77,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ten people will be given this set as a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.77,0:23:38.89,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Only those subscribing to MVS mobile services are eligible for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:41.64,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order from me, Lelouch vi Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.64,0:23:42.08,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,At all costs...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:45.01,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, return it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:48.15,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi Suzaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:49.74,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That fellow is my enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:53.64,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The man who should protect Nunnally became Euphemia's knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:56.16,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the lineup for the Order of the Black Knights is already finalized,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:58.10,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,am I able to accept this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:24:00.48,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Must I dump that unwillingness aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:04.53,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,in order to shape the world according to my wishes?
